parameters: \nd<Oswald>I'm Oswald Turner, the hunter. Nice to meet you all.
\nd<Marcus>Nice to meet you, Mr. Oswald. I'm Marcus,
then why you knocked the bear out just like before?
\nd<Oswald>Long ago, I lived here with my precious wife.
We had a good time together, she always welcomed me when
I got home from my work...
\nd<Oswald>...but someday, when I left to the forest for
hunting, suddenly our house was raided by bunch of enemies,
and one of them was that Bear. I got back home to save my wife
quickly, but it didn't end well...
\nd<Oswald>... my wife, got attacked by that damn Bear,
without any mercy, and I got to fight with it but
couldn't fight any further, I'd lost my all spirit.
Lost my wife was just like losing everything...
\nd<Damian>So that's why you came to the forest to
\nd<Oswald>Yeah, I had to do it for my all emotions.
That was my revenge that I had been harboring for a long
\nd<Oswald>And thanks to you two, my feelings had been
paid off. I can feel better now, well even though
I still feel lost about my wife...
\nd<Marcus>It's our pleasure to help, Mr. Oswald!
Coincidentally, we came at the right time, I guess.
\nd<Oswald>Anyway, what were you doing in that forest?
That forest isn't safe just like the outside, though...
\nd<Marcus>I was doing my Dad a favor, and that's why
my Dad lent me these equipments for myself and my friend.
\nd<Marcus>I was told to look for mushrooms in that forest,
Lumbica Forest. My Dad was going to make concoction, but
lacked for ingredients, so my Dad need me to pick that mushrooms.
\nd<Oswald>Glad you found them, eh? I think your dad will
be proud of you doing a brilliant job for him.
\nd<Damian>I guess it's time. Let's head back to your dad,
\nd<Damian>Thanks Mr. Oswald for the time, for letting us here,
and we're really glad that can help you.
\nd<Oswald>I'm the one who should thank you, without
your help, probably my emotions never going back to just
the old days. Thank you again, Marcus, Damian.
\nd<Oswald>Oh yeah, for one thing, if you have to going
to forest again, and you feel a bit tired, you can take
a rest here, in my house, 'kay?
\nd<Oswald>Of course, you can rest here just like your home.
Just enjoy it and use it.
Now you can learn new skill!
You can save your progress here through this green crystal.
You wanna to save your progress?
Sure, I have to save it right now.
Sure, I have to save it right now.
You can restore your health here, do you want to rest?
You can restore your health here, do you want to rest?
\nd<Oswald>Feel free here, and you can take a rest here
if you feel a bit tired. Enjoy it.
